<font color="#FFFFFF">I invite her here to join us.</font>

225
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,878
<font color="#FFFFFF">Neither dressed</font>

226
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,279
<font color="#FFFFFF">nor undressed.</font>

227
00:15:56,039 --> 00:15:57,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">What else?</font>

228
00:15:57,480 --> 00:16:00,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">Neither hungry nor full,</font>

229
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:05,235
<font color="#FFFFFF">neither in company nor alone.</font>

230
00:16:07,759 --> 00:16:10,115
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can you remember
all of that, one eye?</font>

231
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:16,152
<font color="#FFFFFF">What did the Seer tell you?</font>

232
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:20,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">He said that it's true,
