239
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:08,357
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, Earl Ragnar,</font>

240
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:10,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">I come to you as you desired.</font>

241
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:12,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">Neither dressed nor undressed,</font>

242
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:15,276
<font color="#FFFFFF">neither hungry nor full,</font>

243
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:17,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">neither alone
