she'd cut his balls off.</font>

287
00:21:48,799 --> 00:21:51,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then it's
a good thing she's not.</font>

288
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,959
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen to me, my friend.</font>

289
00:21:54,079 --> 00:21:56,595
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your father and mother
