292
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:32,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">I trust all is to
your satisfaction.</font>

293
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,513
<font color="#FFFFFF">You feed me very well.</font>

294
00:22:35,599 --> 00:22:36,875
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're an important guest.</font>

295
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:41,232
<font color="#FFFFFF">We would like to keep you entertained
