<font color="#FFFFFF">What is it you want, Rollo?</font>

303
00:23:13,599 --> 00:23:15,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is it you really want?</font>

304
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:26,519
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Fenrir, the giant wolf,</i></font>

305
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:29,951
<font color="#FFFFFF">could not be constrained
by any means known to man,</font>

306
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:33,435
<font color="#FFFFFF">so the dwarves forged a chain,</font>

307
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,911
<font color="#FFFFFF">but not from metal.</font>

308
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:40,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nothing made by man
could constrain Fenrir,</font>

309
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:43,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">so they forged it
from the things we cannot see</font>

310
00:23:44,359 --> 00:23:46,032
<font color="#FFFFFF">and the things we cannot hear.</font>

311
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like the breath of a fish,</font>

312
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,789
<font color="#FFFFFF">the sound a moving cat makes.</font>

313
00:23:52,359 --> 00:23:54,078
<font color="#FFFFFF">The roots</font>

314
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">of a mountain.</font>

315
00:23:56,279 --> 00:23:57,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know?</font>

316
00:23:59,039 --> 00:24:00,792
<font color="#FFFFFF">Of course I know!</font>

317
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,359
<font color="#FFFFFF">These things interest me!</font>

318
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like the terrible tricks
of the god Loki.</font>

319
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:09,915
<font color="#FFFFFF">How he turns into a flea
