320
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:12,034
<font color="#FFFFFF">of her precious necklace.</font>

321
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:15,236
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's only a distant ancestor.</font>

322
00:24:21,519 --> 00:24:23,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">I came to ask about Jarl Borg.</font>

323
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">He won't sell.</font>

324
00:24:27,079 --> 00:24:28,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">He wants to make a deal.</font>

325
00:24:29,559 --> 00:24:32,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not interested in deals.</font>

326
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">That would make
it hard for Ragnar.</font>

327
00:24:36,559 --> 00:24:39,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ragnar will come to
the right conclusion</font>

328
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,279
<font color="#FFFFFF">and make the right decision.</font>

329
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:45,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">In any case, there is
someone else in Götland</font>

330
00:24:45,519 --> 00:24:46,749
<font color="#FFFFFF">who looks after my affairs.</font>

331
00:24:47,279 --> 00:24:49,714
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't you care if
the negotiations fail?</font>

332
00:24:53,319 --> 00:24:54,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look!</font>

333
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:33,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am going to die.</font>

334
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:37,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, you are not going to die.</font>

335
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:42,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Seer might think that
he is the only one in Kattegat</font>

336
00:25:42,119 --> 00:25:44,270
