339
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:58,996
<font color="#FFFFFF">I should tell you the truth
about who I really am.</font>

340
00:26:01,519 --> 00:26:03,477
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am Princess Aslaug.</font>

341
00:26:03,559 --> 00:26:06,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">My mother was the
shield-maiden Brunhilde.</font>

342
00:26:09,799 --> 00:26:13,919
<font color="#FFFFFF">Everyone knows the renown
