00:26:20,359 --> 00:26:22,477
<font color="#FFFFFF">Both my parents are dead now,</font>

346
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,997
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I did not know them anyway.</font>

347
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:27,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why did you come along with me?</font>

348
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:30,678
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because I had no choice.</font>

349
00:26:44,079 --> 00:26:45,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why did you do that?</font>

350
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:48,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because I had no choice.</font>

351
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">I hate you.</font>

352
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:49,758
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's disgusting.</font>

353
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:53,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">I could not help myself.</font>

354
00:27:53,079 --> 00:27:55,037
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shall I tell that to Lagertha,</font>

355
00:27:55,119 --> 00:27:56,155
<font color="#FFFFFF">your wife?</font>

356
