360
00:28:09,039 --> 00:28:10,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">Of course I love your mother.</font>

361
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:21,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">Swear to me that it
will not happen again.</font>

362
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:31,518
<font color="#FFFFFF">I swear to you it
won't happen again.</font>

363
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,673
<font color="#FFFFFF">I love you.</font>

364
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:45,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now, go play.</font>

365
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

366
00:29:38,039 --> 00:29:39,473
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

367
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:43,874
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

368
00:29:55,359 --> 00:29:56,874
<font color="#FFFFFF">Athelstan?</font>

369
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:03,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is so weak he cannot eat.</font>

370
00:30:04,799 --> 00:30:07,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pray to the gods,</font>

371
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">please, for him.</font>

372
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait, no.</font>

373
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:21,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">I said no.</font>

374
00:31:33,759 --> 00:31:35,318
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

375
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:36,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lord of lords,</font>

376
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:39,910
<font color="#FFFFFF">we make this offering to you,</font>

377
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">hoping you will
find it pleasing.</font>

378
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:26,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can you try a little more?</font>

379
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gyda.</font>

380
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:19,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">Enjoy!</font>

381
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's wrong with you?</font>

382
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:43,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm carrying your child.</font>

383
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:52,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did the Seer not
