389
00:36:20,239 --> 00:36:21,798
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, he said...</font>

390
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">What did he say?</font>

391
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:36,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">What did he say?</font>

392
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">He will make no compromises,</font>

393
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,114
<font color="#FFFFFF">no deals.</font>

394
00:36:44,719 --> 00:36:47,757
<font color="#FFFFFF">He say you must name
your price for the land.</font>

395
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:50,034
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or?</font>

396
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">He didn't say "or."</font>

397
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:01,195
<font color="#FFFFFF">It seems your mission
has been entirely wasted,</font>

398
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,958
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ragnar Lothbrok.</font>

399
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:06,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">You and your men must leave
here in the morning.</font>

400
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:11,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">Unless you want to
repudiate King Horik,</font>

401
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">renounce your allegiance to him?</font>

402
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,753
<font color="#FFFFFF">I see.</font>

403
00:37:28,199 --> 00:37:29,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">Very well.</font>

404
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,159
