405
00:37:40,159 --> 00:37:41,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">War.</font>

406
00:39:09,079 --> 00:39:10,833
<font color="#FFFFFF">Odin.</font>

407
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:01,835
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, my friend, the die is cast.</font>

408
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">King Horik has
left me no choice.</font>

409
00:40:03,559 --> 00:40:06,836
<font color="#FFFFFF">I must attack him and claim
